text: Fazal Ilahi Chaudhry () (January 1, 1904 - June 2, 1982) was President of Pakistan from August 14, 1973 until he left on September 16, 1978. ==References== Category:1904 births Category:1982 deaths Category:Politicians from Punjab, Pakistan Category:Presidents of Pakistan Category:Speakers of the National Assembly of Pakistan
title: Fazal Ilahi Chaudhry
